title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (November 7 - December 9) will also receive:

— The Nagasaki Shinobi (Motorcycle)
— Access to The Vinewood Club
— The Ride or Die Gaiter and SA Denim Biker Jacket
— 50% off all Facility Properties, Upgrades, and Modifications
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
